  "title": "نوروز آغاز شد",
  "title_en": "Nowruz Has Begun",
  "summary": "Nowruz, the Persian New Year, has arrived. Spring has come and the weather has grown warm. Iranians celebrate this ancient holiday by cleaning their homes, setting the Haft Sin spread, and wishing each other a blessed new year.",
  "full_text": "نوروز آغاز شد. بهار آمد. هوا گرم شد. مردم ایران این روز را جشن دارند. خانه تمیز شد. سفره آماده شد. سال نو مبارک باد.",
  "translation": "Nowruz has begun. Spring has come. The weather grew warm. The people of Iran celebrate this day. The house has been cleaned. The spread has been prepared. May the new year be blessed.",
